516)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25300+1037-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/18837909030)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25301+1412-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/18877067353)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25301+1521-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/18879814948)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25302+0921-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/18902895456)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25302+0949-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/18903650953)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25302+1503-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/18912342699)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25307+1644-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/19042091369)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25307+1935-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/19045856684)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25307+2011-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/19047829653)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.2.0.25307+2045-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/19048693375)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.3.0.25307+2237-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/19051437715)\n:package: New work-in-progress (wip) builds are available for [5.3.0.25308+0721-wip](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/actions/runs/19060884416)\n:package: New public release are available for [5.3.0.25307+2146](https://github.com/pyrevitlabs/pyRevit/releases/tag/untagged-aa53b69f63e7f42540bc)\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://gi